[[File:Clara_Hughes_at_WC_2007_in_Heerenveen.jpg|thumb]]
'''克拉拉·休斯'''（{{lang-en|Clara Hughes}}，{{bd|1972年|9月27日|catIdx=Hughes, Clara}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]女子[[速滑|速滑]]和[[自行车|自行车]]运动员。她在[[1996年夏季奧運會|1996年夏季奧運會]]中獲得兩面銅牌，再於另外三屆[[冬季奥运会|冬季奥运会]]中合共贏得一金一銀兩銅，是世界上唯一一位同时在[[夏季奥运会|夏季奥运会]]和冬季奥运会上同时夺得多枚奖牌的运动员<ref>{{Cite news|title=Clara Hughes's finest hour|url=http://www.cbc.ca/olympics/story/2006/02/25/hughes_newsmaker060225.html|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC Sports]]|date=February 26, 2006|accessdate=2010-02-18|archive-date=2011-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604151827/http://www.cbc.ca/olympics/story/2006/02/25/hughes_newsmaker060225.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Olympic heroes: Double doses of Eddie Eagan|work=Edmonton Sun|url=http://www.edmontonsun.com/sports/vancouver2010/news/2010/02/10/12816621-sun.html|date=February 10, 2010|accessdate=2010-02-18|archive-date=2017-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403181918/http://www.edmontonsun.com/sports/vancouver2010/news/2010/02/10/12816621-sun.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是加拿大唯一一位在冬夏兩項奧運會中贏取獎牌的運動員<ref name=Hesjedal-Hughes-join-2012Olympics>{{cite news |title= Cyclists Ryder Hesjedal, Clara Hughes join Olympic team |url= http://www.cbc.ca/sports/story/2012/06/21/sp-olympics-cycling-canada-road-hesjedal.html |date= June 21, 2012 |author= Jesse Campigotto |publisher= CBC Sports |accessdate= June 29, 2012 |archive-date= 2020-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200924044105/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/story/2012/06/21/sp-olympics-cycling-canada-road-hesjedal.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

她在[[2010年冬季奧運會|2010年冬季奧運會]]的[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會開幕式|開幕儀式]]上擔任[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會加拿大代表團|加拿大代表團]]的持旗手<ref>{{Cite news|first = Shi|last=Davidi |title = 'Someone who is truly remarkable': Clara Hughes named flag-bearer for Vancouver |publisher = Winnipeg Free Press |date =January 30, 2010}}</ref>，並於該屆冬奧的女子5000米短道速滑項目中獲得銅牌；該場賽事也是她最後一次參加奧運速度滑冰比賽<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hughes adds another bronze to incredible resume|publisher=[[Canadian_Online_Explorer|Slam! Sports]]|date=February 24, 2010|accessdate=2010-02-24|url=http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Olympics/2010Vancouver/News/2010/02/24/13013706-qmi.html}}</ref>。

